{"count":1,"next":null,"previous":null,"results":[{"slug":"grappler","name":"Grappler","desc":"You've developed the skills necessary to hold your own in close-quarters grappling. You gain the following benefits:\n- You have advantage on attack rolls against a creature you are grappling.\n- You can use your action to try to pin a creature grappled by you. To do so, make another grapple check. If you succeed, you and the creature are both restrained until the grapple ends.","prerequisite":"Strength 13 or higher","document__slug":"wotc-srd","document__title":"Systems Reference Document"}]}